703770f-a.title: Brooklyn: Concord Street - Duffield Street
703770f-a.text:
177193 Concord Street, north side, from and including Duffield, to,
but not including Gold Streets. The buildings shown are frame except
the last two, numbering 177 to 181. In the foreground, is Gold Street.
October 31, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
